OL,3,CSarah Michelle Gellar leads tributes
OL,4,Cto Buffy co-star Anthony Head: 'I'm
OL,5,Cnot OK'
OL,7,FAmerican actress Sarah Michelle Gellar
OL,8,Fhas led the tributes to her Buffy The
OL,9,FVampire Slayer co-star Anthony Head
OL,10,Fafter the death of the English actor
OL,11,Faged 72.
OL,13,FHead was best known as librarian
OL,14,FRupert Giles in the cult US
OL,15,Fsupernatural TV series, starring
OL,16,FGellar in the the title role, which
OL,17,Fran from 1997 to 2003.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
