OL,3,CSarah Michelle Gellar leads tributes
OL,4,Cto Buffy co-star Anthony Head: 'I'm
OL,5,Cnot OK'
OL,7,FA statement from his daughters,
OL,8,Factresses Emily and Daisy Head, to the
OL,9,FPress Association on Friday revealed
OL,10,Ftheir father had "passed away
OL,11,Fpeacefully of complications due to
OL,12,Fpneumonia".
OL,14,FThe statement also said "his legacy
OL,15,Fwill live on, in the shows he was a
OL,16,Fpart of, and in the audiences that
OL,17,Flove them" as his daughters reflected
OL,18,Fon the impact of his decades-long
OL,19,Fcareer.
OL,26,@rD@ROUtD@JO]vD@YOUyD@JO]
