OL,3,CSarah Michelle Gellar leads tributes
OL,4,Cto Buffy co-star Anthony Head: 'I'm
OL,5,Cnot OK'
OL,7,FGellar, 49, shared a photo of herself
OL,8,Fwith Head, his daughters and their
OL,9,FBuffy co-star Seth Green on Instagram
OL,10,Fas she paid tribute.
OL,12,FShe also included images of her and
OL,13,FHead throughout the years, including a
OL,14,Fmemorable scene during which Buffy
OL,15,Fasks Giles whether life gets any
OL,16,Feasier.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
