OL,3,CSarah Michelle Gellar leads tributes
OL,4,Cto Buffy co-star Anthony Head: 'I'm
OL,5,Cnot OK'
OL,7,FAmong the Buffy cast remembering Head,
OL,8,FDavid Boreanaz, who played Angel,
OL,9,Fdescribed his co-star as a "kind and
OL,10,Fgenerous soul", while James Marsters `
OL,11,Fthe punk-rock vampire Spike ` said the
OL,12,Fdeath left a "hole in the world".
OL,14,FEmma Caulfield, who played reformed
OL,15,Fdemon Anya in Buffy, reflected on
OL,16,Ftheir 27 years of friendship as she
OL,17,Fhailed him as "kind, wise and a guide
OL,18,Fin troubled times".
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@NO]tD@NOUtD@`O]yD@OOUzD@RO]
