OL,3,CSarah Michelle Gellar leads tributes
OL,4,Cto Buffy co-star Anthony Head: 'I'm
OL,5,Cnot OK'
OL,7,FCharisma Carpenter, who starred as
OL,8,Fqueen bee Cordelia Chase, recounted
OL,9,Fmeeting Head in the Buffy production
OL,10,Foffice for the first time and being
OL,11,F"completely thrown off" by how
OL,12,Fdifferent he was to his stuffy
OL,13,Flibrarian character.
OL,15,FThe American actress said: "He had an
OL,16,Fearring, Converse high-tops and a pair
OL,17,Fof loose-fitting, boldly striped
OL,18,Fpants. There wasn't a trace of Giles
OL,19,Fto be found, which was a testament to
OL,20,Fhis gifts."
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@WO]wD@\OU|D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
