OL,3,CSarah Michelle Gellar leads tributes
OL,4,Cto Buffy co-star Anthony Head: 'I'm
OL,5,Cnot OK'
OL,7,FHead also starred in football comedy
OL,8,FTed Lasso from 2020 as former Richmond
OL,9,FFC owner Rupert Mannion, the ex-
OL,10,Fhusband of Hannah Waddingham's
OL,11,Fcharacter Rebecca Welton.
OL,13,FBrett Goldstein, their co-star and a
OL,14,Fwriter on the show, remembered him as
OL,15,F"infinitely charming and kind and fun
OL,16,Fand a joy", adding: "Anthony Head was
OL,17,Fa brilliant actor who played the worst
OL,18,Fperson in the world, which was an
OL,19,Fincredible skill because he was the
OL,20,Fbest person.
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@JO]xD@UOU
