OL,3,CSarah Michelle Gellar leads tributes
OL,4,Cto Buffy co-star Anthony Head: 'I'm
OL,5,Cnot OK'
OL,7,F"He will be sorely missed. Love to his
OL,8,Ffamily."
OL,10,FOther notable roles included the prime
OL,11,Fminister in Little Britain alongside
OL,12,Factor Matt Lucas, who wrote on X that
OL,13,FHead was "unfailingly brilliant, and
OL,14,Falways so kind and warm".
OL,16,FHe played King Uther Pendragon in
OL,17,FMerlin, the father of Prince Arthur,
OL,18,Fwhere he worked alongside award-
OL,19,Fwinning screenwriter and producer
OL,20,FRussell T Davies.
