OL,3,CSarah Michelle Gellar leads tributes
OL,4,Cto Buffy co-star Anthony Head: 'I'm
OL,5,Cnot OK'
OL,7,FDavies remembered Head as an "absolute
OL,8,Fdelight", writing: "He spoke always
OL,9,Fabout his daughters with such love and
OL,10,Fjoy, what a wonderful dad.
OL,12,F"Love and sympathy to Emily, Daisy,
OL,13,Ffamily and friends, he'll be missed
OL,14,Fand remembered across the world. Good
OL,15,Fnight, sir."
OL,17,FKnown for his distinctive baritone
OL,18,Fvoice, Head first rose to fame in the
OL,19,FUK in the 1980s in the Nescafe Gold
OL,20,FBlend television adverts alongside
OL,21,FSharon Maughan.
OL,26,@oD@^OUpD@HO]pD@TOUtD@AOUwD@LO]
