OL,3,CSarah Michelle Gellar leads tributes
OL,4,Cto Buffy co-star Anthony Head: 'I'm
OL,5,Cnot OK'
OL,7,FThe ads, which ran from 1987 to 1993,
OL,8,Fare one of the best-known examples of
OL,9,Fserialised advertising.
OL,11,FHe was also a singer, starring in the
OL,12,F1990 West End revival of The Rocky
OL,13,FHorror Show as Dr Frank-N-Furter, and
OL,14,Frecorded music, including the album of
OL,15,Fthe Buffy The Vampire Slayer musical
OL,16,Fepisode.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
