OL,3,CSarah Michelle Gellar leads tributes
OL,4,Cto Buffy co-star Anthony Head: 'I'm
OL,5,Cnot OK'
OL,7,FHead's role in Buffy made him famous
OL,8,Fin the United States, but he left the
OL,9,Fregular cast during the show's sixth
OL,10,Fseason, only appearing as a guest star
OL,11,Funtil the series concluded.
OL,13,FHe also acted in Motherland, Manchild,
OL,14,FSilent Witness, Spooks, Doctor Who and
OL,15,FMy Family, and in July 2018 he joined
OL,16,Fthe cast of BBC Radio 4 long-running
OL,17,Fdrama The Archers.
OL,19,FHead's long-time partner, animal
OL,20,Fwelfare campaigner Sarah Fisher, died
OL,21,Fin December 2025 aged 61.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
