OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780747879
OL,3,CSarah Michelle Gellar leads tributes
OL,4,Cto Buffy co-star Anthony Head: 'I'm
OL,5,Cnot OK'
OL,7,FFisher was a patron of Holly Hedge
OL,8,FAnimal Sanctuary and an ambassador for
OL,9,FBattersea Dogs And Cats Home alongside
OL,10,Fher husband.
OL,12,FPeter Laurie, the chief executive of
OL,13,FBattersea, said: "Anthony, alongside
OL,14,Fhis late partner Sarah Fisher, gave so
OL,15,Fmuch to our charity, fostering dogs,
OL,16,Fraising awareness of our work, and
OL,17,Fsupporting our events and fundraisers.
OL,19,F"A true champion for all rescue
OL,20,Fanimals, he will be dearly missed by
OL,21,Fall of us."
OL,26,@uD@ROU{D@AOU}D@KO]
